{
  "texts": [
    "The first goal of this study is to assess the status of application segments for the smart energy of buildings.",
    "This part of the study can be categorized as a mapping study.",
    "Then, the second goal of this study is to review the applications and the machine learning techniques identified through the mapping study.",
    "This part of the study can be categorized as a systematic literature review.",
    "The steps of the mapping and systematic literature review are presented below."
  ]
}